#

Baked Gala Apples

40 min
$5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow Fat

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertEasyHealthy

Description

Warm, sweet, and filled with cinnamon goodness, these baked Gala apples are a simple yet delightful dessert that will impress anyone.

Ingredients

  • gala apples: 4
  • brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • oats: 1/2 cup
